comment: Love the app! Transfers are instant and the UI is clean.
Can't log in after the last update—says 'session expired' every time.
Please add biometric login. Typing my password on the bus is annoying.
Fees are too high for international transfers. Competitors are cheaper.
Best banking app I've used. Notifications are on point.
Login keeps failing. Support said clear cache but it didn't help.
Would be great to have spending categories and monthly budgets.
App crashes when I open statements. Using it for 6 months, started last week.
Quick balance check and pay bills in seconds. No complaints.
Why do I pay €5/month for this when basic features are missing?
Face ID works 50% of the time. Often falls back to password.
Card controls (freeze/unfreeze) are super useful. More of this please.
Logged me out randomly and had to reset password. Very frustrating.
Add dark mode. Using it at night is harsh on the eyes.
Interest rates on savings are a joke compared to others.
Smooth experience overall. Only wish there was a desktop version.
Login with fingerprint fails after phone restart. Known bug?
Request: let me nickname my accounts (e.g. 'Rent', 'Fun money').
App is fine but subscription price went up with no new features.
Support was fast and fixed my login issue. Happy customer.
Need export to CSV for my accounts. For taxes and budgeting.
Sometimes stuck on loading after login. Have to force close.
Bill splitting with friends would be a game changer.
Free for basic use, premium is overpriced for what you get.
Clean design and no ads. Refreshing for a banking app.
Two-factor is a pain—codes often arrive late or not at all.
Would love recurring transfers and standing orders from the app.
Crashed during a transfer. Money left my account but recipient didn't get it. Took 3 days to resolve.
Best part is instant notifications. I always know when money moves.
Login page sometimes doesn't load. Only works after 2–3 tries.
Add joint accounts and shared goals. Me and my partner would use it.
Monthly fee for 'premium' when other banks offer same for free. Rethink pricing.
Simple and reliable. Been using it for a year with no major issues.
Password reset link expires too quickly. Had to request it twice.
Request: round-up purchases to nearest euro and save the difference.
App is good but too many upsells for insurance and loans.
Login with Apple/Google would be great. One less password to remember.
No issues so far. Fast, clear, does what I need.
After update, login loop: enter PIN, then it asks again. Unusable.
Please add widget for home screen with balance (with hide option).
Fee for receiving international payments is unfair. Sender already paid.
Card ordering and activation from the app is seamless. Big plus.
Biometric works on iOS but not on my Android. Inconsistent.
Would like scheduled payments—e.g. pay rent on the 1st automatically.
Pricing is transparent. No hidden fees. App could be prettier but it works.
Session timeout is too short. Logged out while reading my statement.
Request: virtual cards for online shopping with custom limits.
Premium tier doesn't justify the cost. Basic is enough for me.
Reliable and fast. Only minor gripe is no in-app chat support.
Login issues after changing phone. Account recovery took a week. Needs improvement.
